description: Reactivate your cells to produce their own Hyaluron and Collagen with NIVEA Cellular Hyaluron Filler Anti-Age Night Cream. Working through the night, when your skin is at its most receptive, the cream helps to fill wrinkles, refine your contours and increase the skins volume.NIVEA Hyaluron Cellular Filler Anti-Age Night Cream features a combination of the cell-activating* ingredients Hyaluron and Bioxilift. With age, the facial skin loses its natural collagen depots, which doesn’t make it look as firm and plump as it used to be. Cells can, however, be reactivated after slowing down. With this night care, your skin cells will be activated to produce their own hyaluronic acid and collagen. The result: Wrinkles are filled, the skin volume is increased and your skin will be plumper. The skin compatibility of this night care has been dermatologically approved. *tested on skin cells.1Quality Ingredients: formula made with Hyaluron and Bioxilift2Effective Results: visibly reduces lines and wrinkles for tangibly firmer skin3Regenerating: works overnight whilst you sleep when your skin is at its most receptive4Lasting Nourishment: activates the skin cells to produce their own Hyaluronic Acid and Collagen5Usage: Perfect for everyday use, even on sensitive skin types to encourage deeply nourished and smooth skin6Directions: apply a generous amount to clean skin, massaging thoroughly around the face, neck, ears, and décolleté
name: Nivea Cellular Filler Anti-age Night Cream Face Moisturiser 50ml
